      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Storage: OneLake  (ADLS Gen2)\n\nBronze: raw JSON files\nSilver: cleaned Delta tables\nGold layer:\n  • dim_learners  (500 rows)\n  • dim_courses   (200 rows)\n  • fact_xapi_events  (50K+)\n  • gold_course_completion\n  • gold_department_skills\n\nSQL Analytics Endpoint\n  pyodbc + AAD token injection\n  SQL_COPT_SS_ACCESS_TOKEN\n\nFabricAnalytics query layer\n  KPIs, funnels, heatmaps,\n  skill gaps, dropout features",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 11,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Storage: OneLake  (ADLS Gen2)\n\nBronze: raw JSON files\nSilver: cleaned Delta tables\nGold layer:\n  • dim_learners  (500 rows)\n  • dim_courses   (200 rows)\n  • fact_xapi_events  (50K+)\n  • gold_course_completion\n  • gold_department_skills\n\nSQL Analytics Endpoint\n  pyodbc + AAD token injection\n  SQL_COPT_SS_ACCESS_TOKEN\n\nFabricAnalytics query layer\n  KPIs, funnels, heatmaps,\n  skill gaps, dropout features",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
