      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Resource: admin-2125-resource\nProject: admin-2125\n\nModel deployments:\n  • gpt-5.4-mini  (chat completions)\n  • text-embedding-3-large  (3072-dim)\n\nManaged Identity\n  → Search Index Data Reader role\n  → FoundryIQ MCP authentication\n\nAgent: educational-consultant\n  PromptAgentDefinition\n  + MCPTool (FoundryIQ KB via MCP)\n  Scope: ai.azure.com/.default",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 11,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Resource: admin-2125-resource\nProject: admin-2125\n\nModel deployments:\n  • gpt-5.4-mini  (chat completions)\n  • text-embedding-3-large  (3072-dim)\n\nManaged Identity\n  → Search Index Data Reader role\n  → FoundryIQ MCP authentication\n\nAgent: educational-consultant\n  PromptAgentDefinition\n  + MCPTool (FoundryIQ KB via MCP)\n  Scope: ai.azure.com/.default",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
