      "updated": 1712880000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Index: course-catalog  (200 docs)\n  • HNSW vector index  (3072-dim)\n  • Hybrid: text + vector search\n  • Semantic re-ranking\n  • OData filters (dept, level, format)\n\nIndexer: scripts/05_index_courses...\n  embed via text-embedding-3-large\n  enrich with Fabric analytics\n\nFoundryIQ Knowledge Base\n  Backed by course-catalog index\n  MCP endpoint (2025-11-01-preview)\n  Autonomous retrieval by agent\n  AZURE_SEARCH_ADMIN_KEY auth",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 11,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Index: course-catalog  (200 docs)\n  • HNSW vector index  (3072-dim)\n  • Hybrid: text + vector search\n  • Semantic re-ranking\n  • OData filters (dept, level, format)\n\nIndexer: scripts/05_index_courses...\n  embed via text-embedding-3-large\n  enrich with Fabric analytics\n\nFoundryIQ Knowledge Base\n  Backed by course-catalog index\n  MCP endpoint (2025-11-01-preview)\n  Autonomous retrieval by agent\n  AZURE_SEARCH_ADMIN_KEY auth",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
