      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Manual RAG mode:\n  embed query → AI Search\n  → inject context → GPT\n  → streaming response\n\nFoundryIQ mode:\n  Foundry Agent + MCPTool\n  → FoundryIQ KB → reply\n  conversations/responses API\n  Server-side history\n\nLearner profile + skill gaps\nDept filter, top-k slider\nSources expander",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
