      "text": "AZURE_CLIENT_ID  /  AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET  /  AZURE_TENANT_ID\nRoles:  Cognitive Services OpenAI User  |  Azure AI Developer  |  Search Index Data Reader\nFabric SQL:  AAD token  →  pyodbc attrs_before={1256: token_bytes}  (bypasses ODBC auth)\nFoundryIQ:  Project Managed Identity  →  Search Index Data Reader on AI Search",
